  "texts": [
    "We identify four main benefits to the incorporation of LLMs in qualitative work: 1. a streamlined and accelerated research process; 2. increased transparency regarding the researchers' background ideas and greater clarity in the construction of concepts and categories; 3. the identification of additional categories and themes note identified by the researchers; 4. increased reliability as the LLM corroborated or challenged the researchers' coding and analysis.",
    "LLM-based generative AI can also be prompted to perform higher-level analyses of qualitative data.",
    "However, the human researcher is still the key to good interpretive research as generative AI cannot be relied on to provide a full or accurate analysis.",
    "Given ongoing and rapid technological developments in LLMs and other forms of accessible generative artificial intelligence, qualitative research practice must take LLMs into account.",
    "The paper consists of two main parts."
  ],
